# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .ai/ — mixed dir: architecture refs are public, everything else is internal
# Explicit block-list for internal .ai/ content. The pre-commit gate enforces
# the allowlist inverse (see scripts/check-doc-location.cjs).
# Public-OK .ai/ files: ARCHITECTURE, INVARIANTS, WISDOM, WISDOM-REFERENCE,
#   AI_ENGINEERING_CONTRACT, RULES, TASK_TEMPLATE.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.ai/*PLAN*.md
.ai/*plan*.md
.ai/*AUDIT*.md
.ai/*DEBT*.md
.ai/*DECISIONS*.md
.ai/*FAILURE*.md
# Exception: FAILURE_MODES.md is a tracked architecture reference (CLAUDE.md
# points at it). Other *FAILURE*.md files remain blocked as internal.
!.ai/FAILURE_MODES.md
.ai/*LAUNCH-BLOCKING*
.ai/*LAUNCH-SCOPE*
.ai/*OPTIMIZATION*
.ai/*IMPROVEMENT*
.ai/*HARDENING*
.ai/*I18N*
.ai/*OPS*
.ai/*VALIDATION*
.ai/*VERIFICATION*
.ai/*COMPREHENSIVE*
.ai/archive/
.ai/plans/

